OL,3,CMouldy Leicester flat 'could kill'
OL,4,Cbaby and toddler, says grandmother
OL,6,FSarah says the mould is everywhere: in
OL,7,Fher bedroom, bathroom and living room
OL,8,Fand is coming through the paintwork
OL,9,Fwhere it was painted over.
OL,11,FSarah says she fears the mould will be
OL,12,Fdangerous for Honey who has a rare
OL,13,Fheart condition called truncus
OL,14,Farteriosus which makes her
OL,15,Fparticularly vulnerable.
OL,17,FHoney has had two open heart surgeries
OL,18,Fand now has a heart from a donor in
OL,19,FAmerica.
