OL,3,CMouldy Leicester flat 'could kill'
OL,4,Cbaby and toddler, says grandmother
OL,6,FShe said: "I'm extremely worried, I do
OL,7,Fthink sometimes something could happen
OL,8,Fto one of the children, especially
OL,9,FHoney.
OL,11,F"It could kill them.
OL,13,F"Nobody should have to live like this,
OL,14,Fespecially my grandchildren."
OL,16,FSarah says the mould has reached
OL,17,Fbehind the children's beds, on their
OL,18,Fmattresses, and has got onto clothes
OL,19,Fwhich they've had to throw away.
