OL,3,CMouldy Leicester flat 'could kill'
OL,4,Cbaby and toddler, says grandmother
OL,6,FHoney and Sophia suffer with coughs
OL,7,Fand colds, which Sarah believes is
OL,8,Fdown to the mould and damp.
OL,10,F"I don't think they care"
OL,12,FSarah says her daughter-in-law spotted
OL,13,Fthe mould two years ago after she
OL,14,Fmoved in.
OL,16,FThe council then came round but only
OL,17,Fmade a temporary fix.
OL,19,FShe said: "I've tried to call the
OL,20,Fcouncil numerous times, I've waited
OL,21,Faround but still nothing has been done.
