OL,3,CMouldy Leicester flat 'could kill'
OL,4,Cbaby and toddler, says grandmother
OL,6,F"They need to pull their finger out,
OL,7,Fhave a bit more compassion because I
OL,8,Fdon't think they care."
OL,10,FLeicester City Council said: "When our
OL,11,Ftenant first reported concerns about
OL,12,Fmould in the property in April 2023,
OL,13,Fwe offered her temporary alternative
OL,14,Faccommodation, but this was declined.
OL,16,F"We did, however, complete some
OL,17,Fremedial works and arranged to go back
OL,18,Fto the property to carry out further
OL,19,Finspections.
