OL,3,CMouldy Leicester flat 'could kill'
OL,4,Cbaby and toddler, says grandmother
OL,6,F"We carried out a further damp
OL,7,Finspection last month and will be
OL,8,Fcontacting the tenant to arrange a
OL,9,Fvisit next week, when we will discuss
OL,10,Foptions available to her and her
OL,11,Ffamily.
OL,13,F"All the required works will be
OL,14,Fcompleted this month, and we will
OL,15,Fcheck to ensure the treatment has been
OL,16,Feffective."
